{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000004", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000004.mp3", "text": "企业停工、停产、员工感染或被隔离，办公场所被限制使用。", "duration": 6.299, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.2029}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000005", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000005.mp3", "text": "这些问题呢给企业，尤其是中小企业的持续经营带来严峻挑战。", "duration": 5.9775, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.1491}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000006", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000006.mp3", "text": "自然灾害、恐怖袭击、疫情等公共突发事件。", "duration": 4.618, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.1205}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000007", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000007.mp3", "text": "二零一九年，仅自然灾害一项，就发生了青海玉树雪灾。", "duration": 5.518, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.1925}
