{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000009", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000009.mp3", "text": "根据二零一四年国家安全蓝皮书，中国国家安全研究报告自一九八九年至二零一四年的二十六年间。", "duration": 9.219, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.173}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000010", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000010.mp3", "text": "面对难以预测但却愈发频繁的公共突发事件？为什么有些企业能够免疫并安然度过？那么有些企业却慌乱应对，甚至危及生存呢？", "duration": 12.87, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.2458}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000011", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000011.mp3", "text": "秦人应该如何应对公共突发事件呢？", "duration": 3.532, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.0996}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000012", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000012.mp3", "text": "首先要我们从事件系统理论认识一下公共突发事件。", "duration": 4.923, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.3151}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000013", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000013.mp3", "text": "根据世界系统理论，我们接下来分析一下公共突发事件的三类属性，第一是强度，包括新颖性、关键性、颠覆性。", "duration": 10.255, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.3849}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000014", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000014.mp3", "text": "第二是时间，也就是事件的时机和时长。", "duration": 4.109, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.2243}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000015", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000015.mp3", "text": "第三是空间，比如实体与事件的距离、事件扩散范围等因素。", "duration": 5.756, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.3679}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000016", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000016.mp3", "text": "从事件强度属性来看，近年来公共突发事件的新颖性较低，但具有极强的颠覆性和关键性。", "duration": 8.3535, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.4677}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000017", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000017.mp3", "text": "人们对疫情、地震、台风、恐怖袭击等事件并不陌生。", "duration": 5.281, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.2408}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000018", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000018.mp3", "text": "相关新闻和反思，频频占据各类媒体的头条。", "duration": 4.091, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.2464}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000019", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000019.mp3", "text": "但企业家或存在赌徒谬误的认知偏见，认为类似公共突发事件不会一再发生。", "duration": 7.521, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.3624}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000020", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000020.mp3", "text": "有的企业家存在过度自负的倾向，认为即便发生也不会影响到自己。", "duration": 6.503, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.5051}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000021", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000021.mp3", "text": "然而，此类事件一旦发生啊，企业的人流、物流、信息流、资金流瞬间易于往常甚至中断。", "duration": 8.37, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.4041}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000022", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000022.mp3", "text": "电力、人员伤亡、厂房受损，通讯及水电中断，道路阻塞，上下游供应链企业停产。 It系统宕机、政府临时管制、市场萎缩等情况。", "duration": 13.158, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.4559}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000023", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000023.mp3", "text": "例如，在二零零一年九幺幺恐怖袭击中。", "duration": 3.718, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.395}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000024", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000024.mp3", "text": "与五百名金融企业员工随世贸大厦的倒塌而丧生。", "duration": 4.805, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.2937}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000025", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000025.mp3", "text": "多家证券公司的交易系统与数据灰飞烟灭。", "duration": 3.99, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.2786}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000026", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000026.mp3", "text": "二零二零年，武汉新冠疫情中，政府出台临时管制措施。", "duration": 4.839, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.3071}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000027", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000027.mp3", "text": "企业停工或有限制复工，旅游业遭受重创。", "duration": 4.228, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.3268}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000028", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000028.mp3", "text": "餐饮业酒店业航空业也岌岌可危。", "duration": 4.279, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.1829}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000029", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000029.mp3", "text": "正是由于近年来公共突发事件的新颖性降低，导致企业缺少忧患意识。", "duration": 6.214, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.5047}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000030", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000030.mp3", "text": "而颠覆性和关键性却很高，导致每一次公共突发事件给企业造成全方位的极大破坏。", "duration": 8.387, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.3976}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000031", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000031.mp3", "text": "从事件的时间属性来看，公共突发事件的发生时机具有极强的随机性。", "duration": 6.298, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.4898}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000032", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000032.mp3", "text": "企业对公共突发事件的预防措施，遵循工业时代的逻辑。", "duration": 5.314, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.2509}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000033", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000033.mp3", "text": "事件的随机性，让企业防不胜防。", "duration": 3.04, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.0727}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000034", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000034.mp3", "text": "此外呢，事件本身及其影响的持续时间通常较长，如人员救治、基础设施恢复时间、社会秩序恢复时间。", "duration": 10.322, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.341}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000035", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000035.mp3", "text": "例如，二零零八年南方雪灾持续一个半月。", "duration": 4.398, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.3119}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000036", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000036.mp3", "text": "全国二十个省均不同程度受到低温雨雪冰冻灾害影响。", "duration": 6.214, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.4168}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000037", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000037.mp3", "text": "连日大雪冻雨，压断电缆电塔，造成多省市长时间停电，多条信号，通讯塔也被压断，造成一些地区多日手机无信号，交通运输停滞半月有余。", "duration": 14.0415, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.3162}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000038", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000038.mp3", "text": "此次新冠疫情爆发，至今已有两个多月。", "duration": 3.124, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.1928}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000039", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000039.mp3", "text": "疫情形势依旧严峻，企业复工一再延后。即使疫情结束，旅游业、会展业等人群聚集性行业在短期内也较难回归常态。", "duration": 12.071, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.3096}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000040", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000040.mp3", "text": "从实体与事件的距离和扩散范围来看啊，公共突发事件对当地非当地企业均会产生显著影响。", "duration": 9.169, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.2615}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000041", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000041.mp3", "text": "伴随着全球化的深入、价值链的变化，企业命运共同体的形成。", "duration": 5.637, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.3341}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000042", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000042.mp3", "text": "企业间的联系愈加紧密，公共突发事件的影响范围很难被控制在发生地。", "duration": 6.859, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.3726}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000043", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000043.mp3", "text": "例如，一九九九年台湾发生七点六级地震，位于新竹的芯片工厂被迫停产。", "duration": 7.046, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.3462}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000044", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000044.mp3", "text": "武汉新冠病毒肺炎疫情导致远在韩国的现代汽车暂停所有在韩生产线。", "duration": 7.402, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.3139}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000045", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000045.mp3", "text": "原因是第三重配件系数的供应商来自中国，而中国零部件供应中断。", "duration": 6.656, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.2594}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000046", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000046.mp3", "text": "现有库存耗尽，造成了现代汽车的连带伤害。", "duration": 4.414, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.5047}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000047", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000047.mp3", "text": "还有一家俄罗斯圣彼得堡的企业，从事轴承、齿轮等机械配件的精加工，也因为中国供应商受疫情影响，没有一家能够正常开工。", "duration": 11.647, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.4631}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000048", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000048.mp3", "text": "导致该企业承受着海外进口商的产品，交付压力，只能进一步等待。", "duration": 5.942, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.4647}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000049", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000049.mp3", "text": "综上所述，公共突发事件的事件属性发生了许多变化，让企业常常忽视此类事件。", "duration": 7.59, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.3771}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000050", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000050.mp3", "text": "因此啊也增大了企业应对此类事件的难度，多数企业缺少足够的免疫能力。", "duration": 6.706, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.3479}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000051", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000051.mp3", "text": "刚才呢我们以事件系统理论为框架，从强度、时间空间三个维度认识了公共突发事件。", "duration": 9.202, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.1631}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000052", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000052.mp3", "text": "基于事件系统理论，企业可以从公共突发事件的事前、事中、事后三个阶段进行考虑。", "duration": 8.32, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.1237}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000053", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000053.mp3", "text": "帮助企业提高自身免疫能力和韧劲。", "duration": 3.464, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.0475}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000054", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000054.mp3", "text": "降低公共突发事件对企业的冲击。", "duration": 3.005, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.1734}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000055", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000055.mp3", "text": "企业应着手建立业务连续性管理机制。", "duration": 3.667, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.0407}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000056", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000056.mp3", "text": "业务连续性管理起源于上世纪七十年代ibm公司的容灾恢复计划。", "duration": 6.689, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.0877}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000057", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000057.mp3", "text": "能够帮助企业识别那些对业务操作产生冲击的潜在威胁。", "duration": 5.534, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.3133}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000058", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000058.mp3", "text": "保障业务操作的连续性，降低各类突发事件对企业持续性经营的冲击。", "duration": 6.536, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.0742}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000059", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000059.mp3", "text": "在公共突发事件发生之前，企业需要居安思危，采取以下四类策略，建立业务连续性管理机制。第一种策略是建立业务连续性治理结构。", "duration": 14.634, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.1309}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000060", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000060.mp3", "text": "有条件的企业可将应急管理委员会，也就是应急会设为常设机构。", "duration": 6.604, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.3494}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000061", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000061.mp3", "text": "并由资深专业人士，比如基础设施人员、it人员、pr人员等担任应急会委员。", "duration": 8.761, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.1361}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000062", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000062.mp3", "text": "自身受限的中小企业可不建立应急会。", "duration": 3.362, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.222}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000063", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000063.mp3", "text": "应急会委员负责分析各类公共突发事件。", "duration": 3.922, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.3392}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000064", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000064.mp3", "text": "识别应急时要恢复的关键业务，包括业务类型、优先级、流程、资源分配、恢复时间目标等。制定应急响应、信息发布等管理计划。", "duration": 14.16, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.1594}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000065", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000065.mp3", "text": "目的是变慌乱无序的应急，为从容有序的应急。", "duration": 4.958, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.1874}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000066", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000066.mp3", "text": "正是得益于此，国内各大商业银行在新冠疫情中表现出色，迅速完成了业务重心与it系统的调整。", "duration": 9.27, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.4006}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000067", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000067.mp3", "text": "将转账、支付类业务、贷款类业务列为优先保障，确保疫情防控所需资金的及时到位。满足了居民日常转账支付需求。", "duration": 11.324, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.39}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000068", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000068.mp3", "text": "以及缺少资金复工的企业的贷款需求。", "duration": 3.583, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.208}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000069", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000069.mp3", "text": "应急会还应取得董事会的授权，在公共突发事件期间，指挥企业的应急处理。", "duration": 7.147, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.5807}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000070", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000070.mp3", "text": "卡尔维克教授曾经研究过这样一个案例。", "duration": 3.107, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.3217}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000071", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000071.mp3", "text": "一九四九年八月五日，美国蒙大拿州的曼恩峡谷发生了一场山火。消防灾难。", "duration": 7.504, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.45}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000072", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000072.mp3", "text": "最有经验的消防员瓦格道奇指挥大家丢弃工具。", "duration": 4.295, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.4}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000073", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000073.mp3", "text": "然而，队长和队员无一听从，最终造成包括队长在内，十三名消防队员的牺牲，仅有瓦格道奇一人幸存。卡尔维克教授对此总结道。", "duration": 12.954, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.4598}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000074", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000074.mp3", "text": "瓦格道奇的指挥是正确的，但是他没有权威。", "duration": 4.397, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.2499}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000075", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000075.mp3", "text": "建立业务连续性管理机制的第二种策略是关键。资源承兑配置。", "duration": 5.569, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.5349}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000076", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000076.mp3", "text": "企业应该围绕关键it系统与数据。", "duration": 3.005, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.199}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000077", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000077.mp3", "text": "关键员工、关键供应链，关键办公场地四个方面，尽早建立备胎。", "duration": 6.435, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.3557}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000078", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000078.mp3", "text": "提高逆境中的韧性，为突发公共事件期间企业的持续经营创造基础条件。", "duration": 7.64, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.1685}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000079", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000079.mp3", "text": "例如，在九幺幺恐怖袭击中，虽然投行巨头摩根士丹利的主数据中心随着世贸大厦倒塌而不复存在。", "duration": 9.627, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.3847}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000080", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000080.mp3", "text": "但是，依靠其异地栽培数据中心和it系统及时启用，公司，第二天便照常工作。", "duration": 7.895, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.3474}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000081", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000081.mp3", "text": "鉴于建立备胎成本较高，中小企业可以配置非对称资源，而不必主备一一对应，以降低备胎的资源投入。", "duration": 12.02, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.3343}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000082", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000082.mp3", "text": "例如，企业可定期将核心客户数据保存成纸质的保密级档案，或将数据备份至云端。", "duration": 7.912, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.3809}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000083", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000083.mp3", "text": "而企业办公场地的备胎，可以是网上办公。", "duration": 3.684, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.1878}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000084", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000084.mp3", "text": "也可以是满足恢复关键业务的最小员工数量的物理场地。", "duration": 5.416, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.3074}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000085", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000085.mp3", "text": "总之，备胎的配置可因此制宜，形式各异，但不可没有。", "duration": 5.874, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.4201}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000086", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000086.mp3", "text": "建立业务连续性管理机制的第三种策略是桌面推演实战练习。", "duration": 5.824, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.2886}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000087", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000087.mp3", "text": "企业不应满足于计划与预案的纸上谈兵。", "duration": 3.667, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.1736}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000088", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000088.mp3", "text": "找到企业应急管理的短板，使企业具有凸性特征，以增强企业的反脆弱能力。", "duration": 7.843, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.2419}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000089", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000089.mp3", "text": "例如，瑞士银行每年都会进行一次反恐演习，采用突袭的形式，事先不提前通知员工。", "duration": 7.589, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.4066}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000090", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000090.mp3", "text": "此外呢还有一次公共卫生事件演习，两次地震演习，多次参与合作伙伴，如中国银联的演习。", "duration": 9.049, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.0915}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000091", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000091.mp3", "text": "瑞士银行在人员伤亡楼宇炸毁数据丢失，通讯与电力中断。", "duration": 5.569, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.2171}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000092", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000092.mp3", "text": "合作伙伴同样遭遇突发事件等情境下，反复演练应对方案，很好的培养了员工的危机意识。", "duration": 8.71, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.21}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000093", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000093.mp3", "text": "应急操作流程，如记鸡肉般刻在员工脑中。", "duration": 4.295, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.3673}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000094", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000094.mp3", "text": "企业还识别出诸如栽备场地网络不稳定、栽备it系统中的客户数据不完整。", "duration": 7.114, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.2768}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000095", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000095.mp3", "text": "业务部门无法提供客户所急需的金融产品，信息发布与流转不畅等多处小失物。", "duration": 8.252, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.0148}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000096", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000096.mp3", "text": "此外呢瑞士银行还邀请心理咨询师就某一类公共突发事件进行分析回顾。", "duration": 7.25, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.2589}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000097", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000097.mp3", "text": "建立业务连续性管理机制的第四种策略是留有一定冗余资源。", "duration": 5.67, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.1597}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000098", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000098.mp3", "text": "企业呢必须保留一定的现金储备、留存收益产能储备等。", "duration": 4.533, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.2185}
{"id": "ZH_B00008_S00000_W000099", "wav": "ZH_B00008/ZH_B00008_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00008_S00000_W000099.mp3", "text": "稻盛和夫在活法一书中有提到，他年轻的时候听过松下性之处的一个演讲。", "duration": 6.367, "speaker": "ZH_B00008_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.4179}
